      <title>Targa Resources 拒绝了其竞争对手 Williams 的收购意向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/targa-resources-rebuffed-takeover-interest-from-larger-rival-williams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，近几个月来，塔尔加资源公司 (Targa Resources Corp.) 拒绝了其较大竞争对手威廉姆斯公司 (Williams Cos.) 的非正式收购意向，这再次表明管道行业持续存在整合意愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/targa-resources-rebuffed-takeover-interest-from-larger-rival-williams</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LME 力争提高月度价格，打破 147 年历史</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所（London Metal Exchange）正计划采取措施，促进其月度合约的电子交易，此举可能会减少其独特的三个月滚动合约的活动，该合约是全球金属行业的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金抹去损失，因美国就业数据疲软增强降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/gold-steady-near-2-500-as-traders-take-stock-after-market-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业岗位数据进一步表明劳动力市场正在降温，为美联储很快开始降低借贷成本奠定了基础，黄金价格抹去了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/gold-steady-near-2-500-as-traders-take-stock-after-market-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员在 JOLTS 之后重新押注美联储降息：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国劳动力市场进一步放缓，华尔街对美联储降息的押注上升，美国国债收益率下跌。随着英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 推动芯片制造商股价上涨，股市出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 22:37:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
